gänge zum Verständnis dieser Prozesse sowie operative Umsetzungsmöglichkeiten entwickelt.  aWhich processes play a role in the transfer of pedagogical concepts into another cultural context? And which possible courses of action arise as a result?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aEthnologie. 4aInterkulturalität. 4aInterkulturelle Pädagogik. 4aKorea. 4aKultur. 4aKunstpädagogik. 4aMusikalische Früherziehung. 4aMusikwissenschaft. 4aOrff. 4aOrtiz. 4aPädagogik. 4aTranskulturieren. 7aEDUCATION / Organizations & Institutions.2bisacsh  aArt Education.  aCulture.  aEducation.  aEducational Research.  aEthnology.  aIntercultural Pedagogy.  aInterculturalism.  aKorea.  aMusicology.  aOrff.  aOrtiz.  aPedagogy.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2017z9783110548242oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839438459zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839438459423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839438459/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2017